      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "**Eligibility** \n\n1. The candidate must be a permanent resident of Himachal Pradesh\n1.  To the girls who are below the poverty line (BPL).\n1.  From each BPL family, only two girl children are eligible.\n1.  All BPL girls who are born after July 5, 2010, can get the benefits of studying till class 12.\n1. A beneficiary girl should not get married before completing 18 years.\n1. The girl who was born after July 5, 2010, will get benefit from this scheme.\n\n",
